data.description:
Located in the highly desired community of Lexington Plantation, this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, boasting a fully fenced backyard, ideal for your summer gatherings. Step into a welcoming entryway leading to a generously sized family room. The kitchen features ample counter space for cooking enthusiasts, a spacious dining area, and a high countertop for extra seating. The owner's suite, along with the additional bedrooms and laundry, is conveniently located on the second floor. NEW ROOF, NEW HVAC, FRESHLY PAINTED! Take advantage of the community amenities, including a pool and playground. Don't miss the opportunity to include this property on your list of must-see homes!
AGENTS-NOT member of LLP MLS?  Call Showing Time to schedule and let them know you are NOT a member and need access.
